Prof. James Nwoye Adichie, the father of international writer and renowned author, Chimamanda Adichie, is dead.<img src="https://i2.wp.com/instablog9ja.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/instablog9ja_20200611_17.jpg?resize=1024%2C1024" /> Adichie passed away after a brief illness on Wednesday night at Chira Memorial Hospital, Awkuzu, Anambra state. He was 88. . He was an Emeritus Professor of Statistics and Mathematics at the University of Nigeria Nsukka (UNN). Original Article Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world.